# 🚀 CampusConnect Pro

Welcome to CampusConnect Pro, a comprehensive management system for university events. This platform allows students to discover and register for events, while enabling organizers to manage them seamlessly.

## ✨ Features

- **Student Portal:** Browse events, register with one click, and view upcoming event tickets (QR codes).
- **Organizer Panel:** Create, edit, and delete events. View attendee lists and take attendance using a QR code scanner.
- **Admin Dashboard:** Full oversight of all users, events, and universities on the platform.

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS
- **Backend:** Netlify Functions
- **Database:** Google Firestore
- **Authentication:** Firebase Authentication

## 🚀 Live Demo

You can view the live deployed version of the project here: [https://campusbro.netlify.app/]
